---
title: Herby Italian Chicken with Roasted Sweet Potato and Vine Tomato Salad
description: Delicious sweet potatoes are a non-starchy carbohydrate, meaning they count towards your 5-a-day, making them a great thing to include in a balanced diet In this comforting and wholesome recipe, Chef Megan has paired sweet potato mash with pan-fried chicken fillets and a fresh Italian-inspired tomato salad for a winning weeknight dish. Quick, simple, and packed with good-for-you ingredients.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-italian-chicken-8c141196-e19ff069.jpg
